text: Požega-Slavonia County is a county in Croatia. The county seat is Požega. ==Administrative divisions== It is divided into: * City of Požega (county seat) * Town of Lipik * Town of Pakrac * Town of Kutjevo * Town of Pleternica * Municipality of Brestovac * Municipality of Čaglin * Municipality of Jakšić * Municipality of Kaptol * Municipality of Velika ==References== Category:Counties of Croatia
title: Požega-Slavonia County
